dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents buildings for Kenosha County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Kenosha_Buildings_2017.gdb.[Kenosha County Buildings / Structures]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.[To digitally represent buildings and structures in Kenosha County.]
